dslRule:
/*!id: eclipse.jdt.ui.refactoring.rename.add-istextselection-true*/
/*!description: Updates RefactoringAvailabilityTester.isRenameElementAvailable() calls to include the 'isTextSelection' boolean argument, setting it to 'true' in specific contexts within JDT UI refactoring actions and quick assists.*/
/*!severity: info*/
org.eclipse.jdt.internal.corext.refactoring.RefactoringAvailabilityTester.isRenameElementAvailable($element)
:: (inClass("org.eclipse.jdt.internal.ui.refactoring.actions.RenameJavaElementAction") && inMethod("setEnabled")) || inClass("org.eclipse.jdt.internal.ui.text.correction.QuickAssistProcessor")
=> org.eclipse.jdt.internal.corext.refactoring.RefactoringAvailabilityTester.isRenameElementAvailable($element, true)
;;

/*!id: eclipse.jdt.ui.refactoring.rename.add-istextselection-param*/
/*!description: Updates RefactoringAvailabilityTester.isRenameElementAvailable() calls to include the 'isTextSelection' boolean argument, propagating it from a method parameter in specific contexts within JDT UI refactoring actions.*/
/*!severity: info*/
org.eclipse.jdt.internal.corext.refactoring.RefactoringAvailabilityTester.isRenameElementAvailable($element)
:: inClass("org.eclipse.jdt.internal.ui.refactoring.actions.RenameJavaElementAction") && (inMethod("doRun", true) || inMethod("canBeRenamed", true))
=> org.eclipse.jdt.internal.corext.refactoring.RefactoringAvailabilityTester.isRenameElementAvailable($element, isTextSelection)
;;

/*!id: eclipse.jdt.ui.refactoring.rename.action.dorun-add-true*/
/*!description: Updates RenameJavaElementAction.doRun() calls to include a 'true' boolean argument when invoked from RenameRefactoringProposal, reflecting internal API changes for text selection context.*/
/*!severity: info*/
$renameAction.doRun()
:: instanceof($renameAction, "org.eclipse.jdt.internal.ui.refactoring.actions.RenameJavaElementAction") && inClass("org.eclipse.jdt.internal.ui.text.correction.proposals.RenameRefactoringProposal")
=> $renameAction.doRun(true)
;;

